snippet.title: Super Pixel Smash - Launch Trailer [VR, HTC Vive]
snippet.description:
Launch trailer for Super Pixel Smash, a fast-paced virtual reality retro-action game. Developed by Rank17, available for HTC Vive. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/super-pixel-smash
